{
  "stem": "1415.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "I was absolutely fascinated by the signs and wanting to read them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "And in that block, I don't know if there were, like, 1,600 or 2,000 women in that block where we were put in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And it was triple-- triple-deckers, as you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And in each section, there were eight women-- I think eight of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "I'm not sure exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "But we were-- if one turned over, all of us had to turn over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "And I remember my mother was with me, and she begged them to put us on the lower bunk, because she knew I-- I-- that I-- that I still wet, I peed.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "So she-- [LAUGHS] she begged them to put us on the lower bunk, and we were put on the lower bunk.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "And every night I used to wet the whole thing, everybody, because we were one on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "If one turned, we all had to turn at the same time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "It was devastating and embarrassing for me, but I couldn't help it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "I just could not help it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "I was very lucky that the women didn't-- didn't tell on me, because I knew if they would tell on me I wouldn't be here to tell the story.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "They all came out of the showers in very sparse clothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "We were given very sparse clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "We weren't given anything back that we-- that we came with naturally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "And we were all deloused, as they called it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "We were all sprayed with that powder always to-- because one of the signs read, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Or-- or one of the signs read, [SPEAKING GERMAN], which means, one louse, your death.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "And it had a double-meaning on that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
